Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.23,0:22:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴爾卡斯!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.97,0:23:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.78,0:23:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.73,0:23:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵殿下…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.73,0:23:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵殿下…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.22,0:23:50.29,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月兒彼方藍色探照燈照耀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.83,0:23:58.74,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然降臨的天使 你究竟是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.20,0:24:06.37,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運的門扉即將開啟　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.68,0:24:12.52,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不放過這令人興奮的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.59,0:24:14.88,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
